24 Hours in Police Custody presented from the Luton Police Station it provides
an insight into the challenges faced by the staff at the police station. The

many many never see for themselves. The documentary/reality series will follow
the team as they respond to 999 calls and arrest suspects as well as watching
around the clock police custody cells. The series will give a close-up of
police interrogation and whether each case can find enough evidence to release
